    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce mandatory life sentences for carrying a knife or other bladed weapon",
        "additional_details": "Knife crime is getting out of hand and we believe police forces don't have the powers or resources to tackle the rise in knife crime. Let's give the criminal a deterrent that will make them think twice, and if they still decide to carry a knife then they should be taken off the streets.",
        "background": "This is very simple, we want anyone caught carrying a knife or other bladed weapon in public without proper reason to be jailed for life. No exceptions, no bail or parole.",
